# the 59TH Rust CLI library variant.  Rust climbs from 58 to 59 documented
# libraries (simplelog via dirble).  Rust **breaks the second triple-tie
# at 58** (Rust=Go=TS-Node=58 since R604) to take SOLO LEAD at 59.  New
# leaderboard: Rust=59, Go=58, TypeScript-Node=58 (Rust SOLO at 59,
# Go+TS-Node tied at 58 — thirteenth time Rust has taken solo lead in
# this round-sequence).  Taxonomy now spans 345 cross-language CLI
# library variants across 84 documented languages.
#
# Pattern: R605 84th language (ATS2 / patsopt) → R606 Rust=59 (simplelog
# THIS) → expected R607 Go=59 → expected R608 TS-Node=59.  This is the
# 1st of 3 leader bumps in the new segment.
#
# This completion EXPANDS Axis 9 (UNIFIED LOGGING) within Rust to FIVE
# variants — Rust now catches TS-Node's Axis 9 lead (both at 5 variants).
# Going forward Rust Axis 6 (errors) at 6 variants remains the deepest
# single-axis coverage of any language in the taxonomy.
#
#   Rust Axis 9 variants:
#     - env_logger (rust-cli/env_logger) — R582 (_trail) — ENV-VAR
