#       activation model
#     - slog (slog-rs/slog) — R586 (_afterburn) — STRUCTURED logger
#       with macro-generated key-value pairs + drains
#     - tracing (tokio-rs/tracing) — R590 (_evebox) — SPAN-BASED
#       contextual logging for async/concurrent code (tokio
#       ecosystem standard)
#     - fern (daboross/fern) — R594 (_bita) — CHAINABLE FILTER
#       DISPATCH builder; .level().chain().chain() composition
#     - simplelog (Drakulix/simplelog.rs) — R606 (THIS) — SIMPLE
#       COMBINATOR-STYLE logger with no env-var dependency;
#       Vec<Box<dyn SharedLogger>> dispatched in parallel
#
# Five Rust Axis 9 variants now span the FULL design space of Rust
# logging:
#   env_logger      = ENV-VAR DRIVEN filter activation (12-factor)
#   slog            = STRUCTURED key-value with drain composition
#   tracing         = SPAN-BASED async-aware contextual logging
#   fern            = CHAINABLE FILTER DISPATCH builder
#   simplelog       = SIMPLE COMBINATOR multi-target init
